author: Chris Baker | cbaker@syracuse.com
title: Ticket prices, on-sale dates announced for Brad Paisley concert at War Memorial
text:
The Oncenter this morning announced ticketing information for the upcoming Brad Paisley concert at the War Memorial in Syracuse.
Paisley performs at the War Memorial Arena at the Oncenter on Saturday, Jan. 30, 2016.
Tickets will range from $48 to $78 (plus fees) and will go on sale Friday, Oct. 30 at 10 a.m.
Tickets will be available via Ticketmaster.com , by phone at 800-745-3000 or at the Solvay Bank Box Office at the Oncenter (760 S. State St., Syracuse).
Presale tickets go on sale Wednesday, Oct. 28 to members of Paisley's fan club .
Paisley's concert is part of his "Crushin' It" world tour, which kicks off Jan. 21 in Arkansas. Eric Paslay and Cam (who performed Thursday night with Darius Rucker at the War Memorial) will open for Paisley.
